---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — GroupsMix"
  description="GroupsMix privacy policy - how we collect, use, and protect your data."
  canonical="https://groupsmix.com/privacy"
  cssFiles={["/assets/css/legal.css"]}
>

        <div class="legal-container">
            <section class="legal-hero">
                <span class="legal-hero__icon">&#128274;</span>
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="legal-hero__subtitle">How we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
            </section>

            <nav class="legal-nav">
                <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
                <a href="/privacy" class="active">Privacy</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
                <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
                <a href="/support">Support Center</a>
            </nav>

            <span class="legal-meta">&#128197; Last updated: March 2026</span>

            <div class="accordion" id="accordion">

                <div class="accordion__item open">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="true">
                        1. Information We Collect
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel" style="max-height:800px">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>We collect different types of information depending on how you interact with GroupsMix:</p>
                            <p><strong>Information you provide directly:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Account details: email address, display name, and profile picture.</li>
                                <li>Group submissions: group name, description, category, platform, invite link, and associated metadata.</li>
                                <li>Reviews and ratings you write for listed groups.</li>
                                <li>Contact form messages and support requests.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><strong>Information collected automatically:</strong></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Usage data: pages visited, search queries, groups viewed, and interaction patterns.</li>
                                <li>Device information: browser type, operating system, screen resolution, and language preference.</li>
                                <li>Network data: IP address (anonymized for analytics), referring URL, and approximate geographic location (country-level only).</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        2. How We Use Your Information
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Provide our services:</strong> Display groups, process submissions, manage your account, and enable community features.</li>
                                <li><strong>Improve the platform:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to enhance user experience, optimize search results, and develop new features.</li>
                                <li><strong>Trust &amp; safety:</strong> Calculate Trust Scores, detect scams, prevent abuse, and enforce our Terms of Service.</li>
                                <li><strong>Process payments:</strong> Handle VIP subscriptions and premium service transactions.</li>
                                <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send account-related notifications, security alerts, and (with your consent) platform updates.</li>
                                <li><strong>Aggregate statistics:</strong> Generate anonymized, non-identifiable platform statistics (e.g., total groups listed, popular categories).</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        3. Data Storage &amp; Security
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard practices:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Database:</strong> All user data is stored on Supabase infrastructure with encryption at rest and in transit (TLS/SSL).</li>
                                <li><strong>Row-Level Security (RLS):</strong> We implement database-level access controls to ensure users can only access their own data.</li>
                                <li><strong>Password security:</strong> Account passwords are hashed using bcrypt and are never stored in plain text.</li>
                                <li><strong>Group invite links:</strong> Encrypted and only revealed to authenticated users after verification checks.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>While we take strong measures to protect your data, no system is 100% secure. We encourage you to use strong, unique passwords and enable any available security features.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        4. Cookies &amp; Local Storage
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>GroupsMix does <strong>not</strong> use third-party tracking cookies. We use browser localStorage for essential functionality only:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Theme preference:</strong> Light or dark mode setting.</li>
                                <li><strong>Saved groups:</strong> Groups you bookmark for quick access.</li>
                                <li><strong>Recently viewed:</strong> Your browsing history within the platform (stored locally, never sent to our servers).</li>
                                <li><strong>Session caching:</strong> Temporary data to reduce loading times and improve performance.</li>
                                <li><strong>Language preference:</strong> Your selected interface language.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>You can clear localStorage at any time through your browser settings. This will reset your preferences but will not affect your account data.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        5. Third-Party Services
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>We use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Database hosting and authentication. <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                                <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — Website hosting, CDN, DDoS protection, and privacy-focused analytics. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                                <li><strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> — CAPTCHA verification to prevent spam and bot abuse.</li>
                                <li><strong>LemonSqueezy</strong> — Payment processing for VIP plans and premium services. <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with any third party for marketing purposes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        6. Data Retention
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide our services:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Account data:</strong> Retained until you request account deletion.</li>
                                <li><strong>Group submissions:</strong> Retained as long as the group is listed. Removed groups are archived for 90 days before permanent deletion.</li>
                                <li><strong>Reviews &amp; reports:</strong> Retained as long as the associated group is listed.</li>
                                <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Anonymized and aggregated data is retained indefinitely. Identifiable usage data is purged after 12 months.</li>
                                <li><strong>Contact messages:</strong> Retained for up to 24 months for support reference.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        7. Children&#39;s Privacy
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>GroupsMix is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that a child under 13 has provided us with personal data, we will take steps to delete that information promptly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        8. Your Rights
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                                <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate information in your profile.</li>
                                <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request permanent deletion of your account and associated data.</li>
                                <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request your data in a structured, commonly used format.</li>
                                <li><strong>Opt out:</strong> Unsubscribe from non-essential communications at any time.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us through our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> or the <a href="/support">Support Center</a>. We will respond to your request within 30 days.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        9. Changes to This Policy
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. When we make changes, the "Last updated" date at the top will be revised. For significant changes, we will notify you via email or a prominent notice on the Platform.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        10. Contact
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please reach out to us through our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> or visit the <a href="/support">Support Center</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
<Fragment slot="scripts">
<script is:inline>
    (function() {
        var theme = localStorage.getItem('gm_theme') || 'dark';
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', theme);
        document.getElementById('theme-toggle').addEventListener('click', function() {
            theme = theme === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', theme);
            localStorage.setItem('gm_theme', theme);
        });
        var items = document.querySelectorAll('.accordion__item');
        items.forEach(function(item) {
            var trigger = item.querySelector('.accordion__trigger');
            var panel = item.querySelector('.accordion__panel');
            trigger.addEventListener('click', function() {
                var isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
                items.forEach(function(other) {
                    other.classList.remove('open');
                    other.querySelector('.accordion__trigger').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
                    other.querySelector('.accordion__panel').style.maxHeight = null;
                });
                if (!isOpen) {
                    item.classList.add('open');
                    trigger.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
                    panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + 'px';
                }
            });
        });
    })();
    </script>
</Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
